{"tid":327343,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點樣沖涼","createTime":"2017-07-18T16:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T19:41:01.000Z","uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6083fc32c086f08bcf8bd7d070207992ee06d8aa","tid":327343,"uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"我自己就用一個大桶裝住熱水用毛巾抹身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣好舒服"},{"pid":"2fab957bb196ea273f18f91576d0772c5ee549d5","tid":327343,"uid":56774,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"你係抹身 不是沖涼"},{"pid":"c234156135f6e1a20d7de2e800657cee5dc66021","tid":327343,"uid":125773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係抹身 不是沖涼</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9008aca1c4bf40bdcd1adb1bf51b8ea9a1656fb2","tid":327343,"uid":1713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係抹身 不是沖涼</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢自己都講左"},{"pid":"b77b99b43040ee76f2abb44dccc414814562f833","tid":327343,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己就用一個大桶裝住熱水用毛巾抹身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣好舒服</blockquote><br />\n咁真係好正，但好細個果陣先會咁做。<br />\n咁做要曬時間，屋企人成日屌我曬水又話我霸廁所耐。成日玩針對，所以平時都盡快沖完，費是又招人話柄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60caa64445c692d49b1e4112c0c06df0bd85e888","tid":327343,"uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T18:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我自己就用一個大桶裝住熱水用毛巾抹身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣好舒服</blockquote><br />\n咁真係好正，但好細個果陣先會咁做。<br />\n咁做要曬時間，屋企人成日屌我曬水又話我霸廁所耐。成日玩針對，所以平時都盡快沖完，費是又招人話柄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我全家到宜家都係咁"},{"pid":"48c19a3f273da61072578d9cbdc331c56b03d665","tid":327343,"uid":60319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T18:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係抹身 不是沖涼</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1d41db128f46813f13259f77ea86550aa35667","tid":327343,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T18:33:48.000Z","msg":"單手洗頭單手拎花灑沖下屎忽同JJ 完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dbfbdd56764c496759ad31276914c2c9281f8b","tid":327343,"uid":128150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T18:39:33.000Z","msg":"一直開住啲水沖全部一次過做哂"},{"pid":"fad51579d29c292a222386f2e84836940e9b7a8e","tid":327343,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T20:32:31.000Z","msg":"一直開住花灑做以下動作，<br />\n淋濕個頭先，洗頭水洗頭<br />\n抹乾水份，上護髮素，停留住唔沖走，<br />\n沐浴露洗身體，上下前後左右，<br />\n洗面奶洗面，<br />\n最後由頭沖到落腳，一次過清哂所有泡泡<br />\n抹身，<br />\n完"},{"pid":"226f561c12e1921d267aae90a05065bf3afb3d82","tid":327343,"uid":23364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T20:33:15.000Z","msg":"有咩花式沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410073ba1a3be0a697f46ae10a8318585efb2236","tid":327343,"uid":58543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T20:41:59.000Z","msg":"倒立"},{"pid":"0a83765b961d9fb715ab66a67bbe094ef62e07c0","tid":327343,"uid":2280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T21:05:07.000Z","msg":"你古人嚟？"},{"pid":"45ade23bb03ababbc3a20f23cec8ed72a402b560","tid":327343,"uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj